Sorry to post again, but I just found something else about my processor 
problem.  While the version of the profile I created that the web 
interface displays still contains my processor, the order.xml file for 
my profile on disk ends with the line: '    <map 
name="write-processors">', and doesn't have any information about my 
processor in it.  Any idea why this would happen?

Thanks for your help,
Xavid Pretzer
